# Wiki Directory

This directory contains the GitHub Wiki pages for the Kubernetes Training repository.

## Structure

- `Home.md` - Main wiki home page
- `_Sidebar.md` - Wiki sidebar navigation
- Other `.md` files - Individual wiki pages

## Contributing

To contribute to the wiki:

1. Edit the Markdown files in this directory
2. Commit your changes
3. Push to the main branch
4. The wiki will be automatically updated

## Local Development

You can preview the wiki locally using any Markdown viewer or by serving the files with a static site generator.

## Guidelines

- Use clear, descriptive titles
- Include code examples where appropriate
- Link to related pages and external resources
- Keep content up-to-date with Kubernetes best practices</content>
